verseObjects.content: + \ft Instead of the second occurrence of \fqa Malkijah \fqa* , some modern versions substitute \fqa Hashabiah \fqa* .
+ \ft Instead of \fqa Bani \fqa* , some modern versions have \fqa Bigvai \fqa* .
+ \ft Instead of \fqa Among the sons of Binnui: Shimei \fqa* , some modern versions have \fqa Bani, Binnui, Shimei \fqa* .
+ \ft Instead of \fqa Maknadebai \fqa* , some modern versions have \fqa Among the descendants of Zaccai \fqa* .
+ \ft Instead of \fqa by whom they had sons \fqa* , some modern versions have \fqa but sent them away with their sons \fqa* .
